WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.010
In this dream, the Lord showed me

00:00:04.020 --> 00:00:06.170
a massive earthquake that was

00:00:06.180 --> 00:00:08.750
going to happen in America. It was

00:00:08.750 --> 00:00:08.760
the New

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:12.770
Madrid fault, and this was

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:15.770
literally the largest

00:00:15.780 --> 00:00:18.050
earthquake that had ever happened on the

00:00:18.060 --> 00:00:21.109
Earth. Whenever I saw it in my

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:25.370
dream, it happened right by the

00:00:25.380 --> 00:00:28.009
Mississippi River, and

00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:30.170
it split the Mississippi River and

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:32.990
made it bigger.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.690
All the bridges that were on the

00:00:35.700 --> 00:00:38.150
Mississippi River collapsed, and they

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:40.310
were all down. The Lord showed

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:43.310
me things were on fire; it was

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:46.369
total devastation.

00:00:46.379 --> 00:00:48.830
I could see it went clear down to

00:00:48.830 --> 00:00:48.840
the

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:51.229
New Orleans area and clear

00:00:51.239 --> 00:00:53.930
up into the Chicago area. It was

00:00:53.940 --> 00:00:56.930
massive. As

00:00:56.930 --> 00:00:56.940
I said,

00:00:56.940 --> 00:01:00.110
all the bridges fell,

00:01:00.110 --> 00:01:00.120
so

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:03.229
there was no way for semi-trucks to

00:01:03.239 --> 00:01:05.690
go from east to west.

00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:09.530
They brought in these bridges

00:01:09.530 --> 00:01:09.540
from

00:01:09.540 --> 00:01:11.690
the Army; they were like floating

00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:13.670
bridges. The Army brought them in and

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:16.310
put them in all up and down

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.649
where the highways were, trying to make

00:01:18.659 --> 00:01:20.690
it so trucks could come in and out

00:01:20.700 --> 00:01:23.149
for emergencies. But they couldn't get

00:01:23.159 --> 00:01:25.310
the trucks from east to west, so they

00:01:25.320 --> 00:01:27.289
brought in planes.

00:01:27.299 --> 00:01:29.690
They flew the

00:01:29.700 --> 00:01:34.130
food into cities where the

00:01:34.130 --> 00:01:34.140
semi-trucks

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:35.569
couldn't get back and forth,

00:01:35.579 --> 00:01:37.130
bringing the food in

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:39.530
humongous cargo

00:01:39.540 --> 00:01:41.870
planes so

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:43.910
that the food could get throughout

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.370
all the cities in America.

00:01:46.370 --> 00:01:46.380
In

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:48.469
another dream, the Lord showed

00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:52.249
me massive helicopters,

00:01:52.259 --> 00:01:54.830
Chinook helicopters, and they were flying

00:01:54.840 --> 00:01:57.590
from the west. I stood on the

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:00.410
back porch in my dream and I could

00:02:00.420 --> 00:02:04.670
visibly smell fire in

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:08.270
the air. It was so strong; it

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:09.710
was like the

00:02:09.710 --> 00:02:09.720
haze

00:02:09.720 --> 00:02:11.270
you see from a fire

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:13.670
whenever there is a grass fire.

00:02:13.670 --> 00:02:13.680
I

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.650
could hear the helicopters

00:02:15.660 --> 00:02:19.070
flying low, and they were all coming

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:22.430
in lines, in

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:22.440
formation.

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:24.229
The helicopters

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:26.030
were coming from the West Coast

00:02:26.030 --> 00:02:26.040
and

00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:27.589
going to the East Coast.

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:30.110
Where I live is in the

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:32.570
central part of America, so you could

00:02:32.580 --> 00:02:34.790
hear them coming.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:37.790
They were so loud because there were so

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:40.610
many of them at a time, all

00:02:40.610 --> 00:02:40.620
flying

00:02:40.620 --> 00:02:43.070
in formation. There

00:02:43.070 --> 00:02:43.080
were

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.750
probably 30 or 40 of them at a time,

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:44.760
and

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:46.850
it would

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:51.050
shake the houses.

00:02:51.060 --> 00:02:53.930
I didn't watch

00:02:53.940 --> 00:02:57.050
TV in the dream, but I knew that

00:02:57.060 --> 00:02:59.630
it was just like a 9/11 event; it was that

00:02:59.640 --> 00:03:01.430
big, something that shook

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:04.729
America. Everything

00:03:04.739 --> 00:03:06.830
was quiet. I could look across

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:09.050
at my neighbors, but nobody was outside;

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:11.270
they were all inside watching

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:15.170
what happened on TV. Then

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:18.410
the Lord took my eyes

00:03:18.420 --> 00:03:22.670
in the dream to a stone lion's face.

00:03:22.670 --> 00:03:22.680
I

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:26.030
was

00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:26.040
asking,

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:28.670
'What is that?'because

00:03:28.670 --> 00:03:28.680
I saw

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:31.250
the stone

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:35.270
lion face. All of a sudden in the

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:38.750
dream, He said, 'Look at the Stock

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:40.850
Exchange, the New York Stock

00:03:40.850 --> 00:03:40.860
Exchange.'I

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:43.610
didn't know where this lion

00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:47.270
face was, so I woke up the next day and

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:50.449
looked up

00:03:51.239 --> 00:03:53.270
the Stock

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:55.670
Exchange. On the top of the building, there

00:03:55.670 --> 00:03:55.680
are

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.250
lions all along the top, and it was

00:03:58.260 --> 00:04:01.550
the exact lion. In the

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:04.430
dream, I could see the streets of New

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:07.070
York, and they were completely desolate. I

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.869
could see tumbleweeds, which was weird

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:11.449
because I know there are no tumbleweeds in

00:04:11.459 --> 00:04:14.210
New York, but I saw them going

00:04:14.220 --> 00:04:16.610
down the street. It was desolate;

00:04:16.620 --> 00:04:19.189
there was nobody moving around. It was

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:22.189
completely blank, like the

00:04:22.199 --> 00:04:24.770
people had all gone and were hiding out,

00:04:24.780 --> 00:04:27.290
because the whole

00:04:27.300 --> 00:04:28.790
government and everything was shut down

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.890
again, kind of like COVID was. It was

00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:33.050
really weird.

00:04:35.220 --> 00:04:38.330
For

00:04:38.330 --> 00:04:38.340
a

00:04:38.340 --> 00:04:40.670
long time, those helicopters

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:42.909
were going towards the Mississippi area.

00:04:42.919 --> 00:04:46.249
Then the Lord showed me another

00:04:46.259 --> 00:04:48.469
earthquake; it was like

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:51.650
an aftershock that happened by the Texarkana

00:04:51.660 --> 00:04:54.950
area and went clear up to Tulsa,

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:57.590
Oklahoma. I could see that it was

00:04:57.600 --> 00:04:59.150
probably a

00:04:59.150 --> 00:04:59.160
magnitude 6

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:02.090
or bigger. But the one that

00:05:02.100 --> 00:05:04.610
hit the Mississippi Valley area was like

00:05:04.620 --> 00:05:09.170
a 10.0. I could see

00:05:09.180 --> 00:05:12.230
that all the houses built on

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:14.450
cinder

00:05:14.450 --> 00:05:14.460
blocks—houses

00:05:14.460 --> 00:05:17.210
not on a flat

00:05:17.210 --> 00:05:17.220
slab—were

00:05:17.220 --> 00:05:20.210
completely destroyed. In this,

00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:23.629
1,800 people died. The Lord

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:24.950
was showing me the people who had

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:28.010
perished in the dream where all of the

00:05:28.020 --> 00:05:30.110
houses were completely leveled and

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:32.930
flattened from this massive earthquake.

00:05:35.220 --> 00:05:37.370
I don't know why it happens

00:05:37.370 --> 00:05:37.380
or

00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:40.370
when it happens; all I know is that I

00:05:40.380 --> 00:05:42.770
saw this and have prayed over

00:05:42.770 --> 00:05:42.780
it.

00:05:42.780 --> 00:05:45.529
I feel that it's about to happen soon.

00:05:45.539 --> 00:05:47.870
Like I said, it could happen in the

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:49.790
fall, it could happen in the spring,

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:51.350
or it could be years from now.

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:53.749
I just see these things; the Lord

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:55.550
gives them to me, and I pray over them. It

00:05:55.550 --> 00:05:55.560
was

00:05:55.560 --> 00:05:58.430
just something

00:05:58.440 --> 00:06:02.090
heavy on my heart to share. If

00:06:02.100 --> 00:06:04.969
you have seen this or

00:06:04.979 --> 00:06:06.650
heard of anyone who has, you

00:06:06.660 --> 00:06:08.390
can comment in the comment

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:11.629
section. I appreciate

00:06:11.639 --> 00:06:13.010
you following me.

00:06:13.020 --> 00:06:14.749
I have more things that I

00:06:14.759 --> 00:06:16.249
want to share, but I want to do it

00:06:16.259 --> 00:06:19.249
on separate videos for what I feel

00:06:19.259 --> 00:06:21.110
the Lord has shown me is coming.

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:22.909
I really appreciate it.

00:06:22.919 --> 00:06:26.600
Thank you all very much. Bye-bye.

